Are you looking for some of the best BBQ on the planet? Then you need to take a trip to Houston, Texas. Now Houston has deep BBQ roots and is even noted as the birthplace of brisket, so you already know there are going to be a bunch of BBQ spots claiming to wear the crown at every turn. So to help you navigate your trip to H-Town here were some of my favourites spots, and menu items. Huge shoutout to the @visit_houston team for helping me explore this food lover‚Äôs heaven on earth. And thanks to @thecuriouscreature for taking on this task with me and keeping up at every tray lol.
Also thanks to all of the BBQ spots who welcomed us with open arms and sent me home with a full belly!

Question, do you pour syrup on your Chicken & Waffles? Or just on your Waffles?

This past January I finally got to attend The Opulent Brunch by @authentiquedelights . Let me tell y‚Äôall I wish I had a Time Machine so I go back and hit up all the previous ones I missed. This may be the best brunch experience in Toronto. Chef Bri is full of incredible energy and immense culinary skill. 

These Chicken & Waffles were perfect. Tender, crispy and flavourful Chicken, paired with perfectly made Waffles and a sweet and spicy Habanero Syrup. 

Stay tuned for more delicious content from this incredible Brunch, cuz I have more to share.

Which Chef put together the more delicious looking Super Bowl Wings Inspired Spread? Team Drums led by Chef @monwahbs or Team Flats led by Chef @howardseivright ?

We all know that no event celebrates the spirit of competition like the Super Bowl. And we all know that food is a major part of that event. 

But did you know that there is a an even fiercer competition that has been going on between food lovers even before the first Super Bowl was played?

This battle is the battle for wing supremacy. Drums or Flats. The debate over which is the better bite is more intense than any football fans love for their favorite team and their despising of their rivals. 

So I got some @pintysfoods wings and two of my favourite chefs to battle it out by making the most appetizing Super Bowl spreads possible. 

We had a drafts, wing related trivia, and a lot of food and a lot of fun. Check it out!!!

#EatFamous #PintysFoods #DrunsorFlats #SuperBowlFood #NFLCanada
